org.vaadin.addons.lazyquerycontainer

Class CompositeItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vaadin.addons.lazyquerycontainer.CompositeItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.vaadin.data.Item, Serializable

    public final class CompositeItem
extends Object
implements com.vaadin.data.Item
    CompositeItem enables joining multiple items as single item. CompositeItem contains PropertysetItem as default item to support adding and removing of properties.
    Author:
    Tommi Laukkanen
